## ğŸ’¡ How to Submit Feature Requests

Going forward, here's how to suggest new features:

### Option 1: GitHub Issues (Organized Tracking)
1. Visit our [consciousness-bugs repository](https://github.com/overkor-tek/consciousness-bugs/issues)
2. Click "New Issue"
3. Title format: `[FEATURE REQUEST] Your feature name`
4. Include:
   - Clear description of the feature
   - Why it would be valuable
   - How you envision it working
   - Any concerns or considerations

### Option 2: Community Discussion (Brainstorming)
- Start conversations in our community channels
- Get feedback before submitting a formal request
- Build consensus around ideas

### Option 3: Vote on Existing Requests
- Comment on existing feature requests with your thoughts
- Use ğŸ‘ reactions to show support
- Add your use cases and ideas

## ğŸ—³ï¸ Feature Prioritization

We'll prioritize features based on:
- **Community Interest** - How many people want it?
- **Impact** - Will it significantly improve the experience?
- **Feasibility** - Can we build it with current resources?
- **Alignment** - Does it fit the project vision?

Features with high community engagement will move to the top of the roadmap!

